quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Ãdãwa sun ƙaryata Manzanni
  26,124,"A lõkacin da ɗan'uwansu, Hũdu ya ce musu, \"Bã zã ku yi taƙawa ba"
  26,125,"Lalle ne ni, zuwa gare ku, haƙĩƙa, Manzo ne, amintacce"
  26,126,"Sabõda haka ku bi Allah da taƙawa, kuma ku yi mini ɗã'ã"
  26,127,"Kuma bã ni tambayar wata ijãra a kansa. Ijãrãta ba ta zama ba, fãce daga Ubangijin halittu"
  26,128,"Shin, kunã yin ginin sitadiyo* a kõwane tsauni ne, kunã yin wãsa"
  26,129,"Kuma kunã riƙon matsãrar ruwa, tsammãninku, ku dawwama"
  26,130,"Kuma idan kun yi damƙa, sai ku yi damƙar kunã mãsu tanƙwasãwa"
  26,131,"To ku bi Allah da taƙawa, kuma ku yi mini ɗã'ã"
  26,132,Ku ji tsõron wanda Ya taimake ku da abin da kuka sani
  26,133,Ya taimake ku da dabbõbin ni'ima da ɗiya
  26,134,Da gõnaki da marẽmari
  26,135,"Lalle ne nĩ, inã ji muku tsõron azãbar wani yini mai girma"
  26,136,"Suka ce: \"Daidai ne a kanmu: Kã yi wa'azi kõ ba ka kasance daga mãsu wa'azi ba"
  26,137,Wannan abu bai zamõ ba fãce hãlãyen* mutãnen farko
  26,138,Kuma mũ ba mu zama waɗanda ake yi wa azãba ba
  26,139,"Sabõda haka suka ƙaryata shi, sai Muka halakar da sũ. Lalle ne a cikin wannan akwai ãyã, kuma mafi yawansu ba su kasance mãsu ĩmãni ba"
  26,140,"Kuma lalle ne, Ubangijinka, haƙĩƙa, Shi ne Mabuwãyi, Mai jin ƙai"